Denmark Supports No-Fly Zone Over Libya, Foreign Minister Says

-- B y   T a s n e e m   B r o g g e r
-- 
2011-03-14T06:18:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/denmark-supports-no-fly-zone-over-libya-foreign-minister-says.html
  Denmark  supports imposing a no-fly
zone over  Libya , Foreign Minister Lene Espersen said.    “I welcome the  Arab League ’s decision to urge the  Security
Council  to impose a no-fly zone,” Espersen said in a statement
on the ministry’s website yesterday. “I share the League’s
concern over the Qaddafi regime’s continued attackes against its
own people.”  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
